StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetProspectIdByNwaIntId]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@NwaId int AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT p.ProspectId FROM [USMC].[Prospect] p INNER JOIN [MCRISS].[dbo].[NWA] nwa on p.nwaid = nwa.rowguid WHERE nwa.Nwa_Id = @NwaId
END
